data.description: Charming Victorian 3 bedroom and 2 bath home, conveniently located on a corner lot in the heart of Canon City. This Victorian gem is  just steps and blocks away from schools, tennis courts, park and hospital. This beauty is waiting for you to restore back to its former glory. High ceilings and Victorian accents through out the home. Check out the garden skylight in the downstairs bathroom, true spa atmosphere.There is a 3 car detached garage with shop and a studio room above the garage. The studio has electricity and dry walled in and carpet. 2 fenced in court yards that offer privacy for tranquil moments or outdoor gatherings. Canon City is termed as the banana belt of Colorado offering temperate temperatures year round, also a little over a hour away you can enjoy skiing at Monarch. 1 hour from Colorado springs. Garage and shop measure 24'x32' Studio room measure 31'4"x11'10".
